    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Top, tail, peel and finely chop your <strong>carrot[s]</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> and<strong> carrot</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and carrot are beginning to soften, add your <strong>meat-free mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) to the pan and increase the heat to high</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min further or until browned all over, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>While the meat-free mince is cooking, add your <strong>pasta </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the pasta for 7-9 min (10-12 min for wholewheat) or until cooked with a slight bite, then drain and return to the pot until serving</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [200ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>stock</strong></p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> stock</strong>, <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong>, <strong>dried basil </strong>and<strong> dried oregano </strong>to the pan</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 4-5 min further or until thickened \u2013 this is your <strong>meat-free mince bolognese</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/simply-perfect-meat-free-mince-wholewheat-spag-bol/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free mince bolognese </strong>over the<strong> pasta</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Keep an eye out for it on the Everyday Favourites section of our menu.</span></strong></p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
